00:20:34,811 --> 00:20:39,192
It's worth saying that sharing content, teaching people,

377
00:20:39,192 --> 00:20:40,273
and helping.

378
00:20:40,894 --> 00:20:44,020
create a system of theory and knowledge

379
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:45,263
that other people can pull from

380
00:20:45,263 --> 00:20:48,429
and hopefully make even better games and levels

381
00:20:48,429 --> 00:20:50,193
is a worthwhile pursuit.

382
00:20:50,193 --> 00:20:51,736
And I think we should celebrate it more.

383
00:20:53,294 --> 00:20:55,436
So I've learned a lot by sharing my work,

